{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"843febf00a","title":"考虑作必要让步，避免破裂两党团结叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52682e0665","index":0,"year":1940,"month":3,"day":15,"articleId":"843febf00a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"111433d486","type":"paragraph","text":"考虑作必要让步，避免破裂两党团结叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"843febf00a"},{"id":"9ed2282da2","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年3月15日）朱、彭二同志蒋、卫已下令庞炳勋、范汉杰、刘勘、陈铁各部主力集中于太南周国，并有从陇海路加调六个师渡河讯，请兄等密切注意此事之严重性，考虑对蒋、卫作必要让步，避免因此破裂两党团结。请你们考虑让出陵川、合润、林县一线的问题","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"843febf00a"},{"id":"c1919b38e9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛王","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"843febf00a"},{"id":"51d57903f1","type":"paragraph","text":"十五日[1]这是毛泽东和王夜祥关于保护两党团结，作出必要让步问题给来德、彭德怀的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"843febf00a"}],"page":{"id":"a96db11366","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"843febf00a","start":480,"end":480}}}},"__N_SSG":true}